msgid ""
"The selected path is removed from the pool and its data is copied back into "
"the pool, where mergerfs redistributes it across the remaining branches."
msgstr ""

msgid "Unit"
msgstr "ຫົວໜ່ວຍ"

msgid "When editing a pool, a reboot may be necessary to apply changes."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອແກ້ໄຂພູລ, ອາດຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໄດ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນລະບົບໃໝ່ (reboot) "
"ເເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງ."

msgid ""
"When enabled, files are removed from the detached disk once they have been "
"copied into the pool."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"When the minimum free space is reached on a filesystem it will not be "
"written to unless all the other filesystem also has reached the limit."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອພື້ນທີ່ວ່າງຕ່ຳສຸດໃນລະບົບໄຟລ໌ໃດໜຶ່ງເຕັມແລ້ວ, "
"ມັນຈະບໍ່ຖືກຂຽນຂໍ້ມູນລົງໄປຕື່ມ ຈົນກວ່າລະບົບໄຟລ໌ອື່ນໆທັງໝົດຈະຮອດຂີດຈຳກັດຄືກັນ."

